[Vanilla Void Gourmet x Soowoonjapbang]
'Taste the noble cuisine passed down for 500 years!'

This is VV x SWJB NFT with IRL benefit.
 1. Each project itself, is a collectible NFT art piece, limited edition!
 2. IRL benefits 100% include, including the invitation to SWJB pop-up at Seoul
 3. Future benefits such as exclusive reservation rights to Andong SWJB.

[IRL meet-up details]
Date: Sunday, November 27th, 2022
Venue: Nana (5 Gyedong-gil, Jongno-gu, Seoul)
